CPP08/ex01

	STL is allowed and you have to use it
	Algorithm library is allowed and have to use it

	Span Class
		store a max of N unsigned int
			only ctor value
		methods:
			addNumber()
				add a single number to the Span
					until it's fill of course, if it's full, throw an exception
			shortestSpan()	
				shortest distance between two numbers	
				if there is 0 or 1 numbers throw exception 
			longestSpan()
				longest distance between two numbers	
				if there is 0 or 1 numbers throw exception 
			
		test with 10,000 or more numbers


